  "original_title": "\u0dad\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dc3\u0dca\u0dad\u0dc0\u0dcf\u0daf\u0dba \u0dc0\u0dd0\u0dc5\u0dd0\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc0\u0dd3\u0db8\u0dda \u0db4\u0db1\u0dad\u0da7 \u0db8\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0dd3 \u0d9c\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dba\u0db1 \u0db8\u0dbb\u0dca\u0daf\u0db1\u0dba\u0da7 \u0d91\u0dbb\u0dd9\u0dc4\u0dd2\u0dc0 \u0da2\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dd3\u0dc0\u0dcf \u0dba\u0db1\u0dc0\u0dcf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Geneva is going against the crackdown under the guise of the Prevention of Terrorism Act",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Ceylon Teachers Association said that measures are being taken to make the suppression of people's opposition using the Prevention of Terrorism Act a major issue at the 51st Geneva Human Rights Conference to be held in September. General Secretary Joseph Stalin said today (23).",
        "Mr. Stalin said this at the special press conference held yesterday at Maradana Social and Peace Center organized by the Inter-University Student Council.",
        "Mr. Mujibar Rahman, Member of Parliament of the Sami People's Force, said at the press conference that Mr. Ranil Wickremesinghe is using the Prevention of Terrorism Act to control the current popular uprising and that shows the duplicity of Mr. Wickremesinghe.",
        "The press conference was attended by many political and civil activists including Pubudu Jayagoda, Education Secretary of Vanguard Socialist Party, Duminda Nagamuwa, Organizing Secretary of Vanguard Socialist Party, Eranga Gunasekara, National Organizer of Socialist Youth Organization and actor Jehan Appuhami."
      ],
